title: Ranking NFL backfields
itunes:title: Ranking NFL backfields
description:
A room filled with heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler -- react to the latest news from around the league, including Dez Bryant's contract situation (4:57) and more notable retirements. Then, the guys discuss which team will have the best backfield in 2015 (23:04).

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
